    "headline": "Ulta Beauty Earnings Were Ugly. We’re Pulling Our Recommendation.",
    "summary": "Beauty is subjective, but it’s hard to paint a pretty picture about  Ulta Beauty  stock after its recent quarter.  Ulta has been a long-term winner, more than doubling its shares since the pandemic through its highs in February.  Investors are concerned that guidance implies earnings per share growth and that improved margins, based in part on reduced ‘shrink,’ or industry-speak for theft, isn’t sustainable.",
